# Тесты формализации «Claude Family Pro»

Каждый скоуп-тест фиксирует ожидаемый выход модели через `assertion`, поэтому
`catala interpret` падает с ненулевым кодом на любой регрессии. Покрыты все ветки
`if/then/else` модели и все зафиксированные интерпретации двусмысленностей.

> Using Claude_family_pro

## §1.2 — Нормализация токенов

По 1000 токенов каждого типа: 1000·1 + 1000·0.1 + 1000·1.25 + 1000·5 + 1000·5 = 12350.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestNormalization:
  output normalized content decimal
  n scope Claude_family_pro.TokenNormalization
scope TestNormalization:
  definition n.usage equals Claude_family_pro.TokenUsage {
    -- input_uncached: 1000.0
    -- input_cache_read: 1000.0
    -- input_cache_write: 1000.0
    -- output_regular: 1000.0
    -- output_thinking: 1000.0
  }
  definition normalized equals n.normalized
  assertion normalized = 12350.0
```

## §2 — Абонентская плата и включённый объём

Обычный период: полная плата, полный объём, перенос разрешён.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestAllowanceNormal:
  output fee content money
  output included content decimal
  output carry_ok content boolean
  a scope Claude_family_pro.PeriodAllowance
scope TestAllowanceNormal:
  definition a.is_termination equals false
  definition a.active_days equals 30
  definition a.days_in_month equals 30
  definition fee equals a.subscription_fee
  definition included equals a.included_volume
  definition carry_ok equals a.carryover_allowed
  assertion fee = $2,490.00
  assertion included = 12000000.0
  assertion carry_ok = true
```

Расторжение в середине (15 из 30 дней): плата и объём пополам, перенос запрещён.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestAllowanceTerminationHalf:
  output fee content money
  output included content decimal
  output carry_ok content boolean
  a scope Claude_family_pro.PeriodAllowance
scope TestAllowanceTerminationHalf:
  definition a.is_termination equals true
  definition a.active_days equals 15
  definition a.days_in_month equals 30
  definition fee equals a.subscription_fee
  definition included equals a.included_volume
  definition carry_ok equals a.carryover_allowed
  assertion fee = $1,245.00
  assertion included = 6000000.0
  assertion carry_ok = false
```

Расторжение с округлением вниз до 100 000 НТ (10 из 31 дня):
объём 12M·10/31 = 3 870 967.7 → вниз до 3 800 000; плата 2490·10/31 = 803.2258 → 803.22.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestAllowanceTerminationRounding:
  output fee content money
  output included content decimal
  a scope Claude_family_pro.PeriodAllowance
scope TestAllowanceTerminationRounding:
  definition a.is_termination equals true
  definition a.active_days equals 10
  definition a.days_in_month equals 31
  definition fee equals a.subscription_fee
  definition included equals a.included_volume
  assertion included = 3800000.0
  assertion fee = $803.22
```

## §3.3 + §4 — Овераж и перенос остатка

Под включённым объёмом, остаток переносится (не капнут): потребление 10M, перенос 2M.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestOverageUnderIncluded:
  output overage content decimal
  output carry content decimal
  o scope Claude_family_pro.OverageComputation
scope TestOverageUnderIncluded:
  definition o.total_consumption equals 10000000.0
  definition o.carried_balance equals 0.0
  definition o.included_volume equals 12000000.0
  definition o.carryover_allowed equals true
  definition overage equals o.overage
  definition carry equals o.carryover_to_next
  assertion overage = 0.0
  assertion carry = 2000000.0
```

Перенос капается на 20% (потребление 8M → неизрасходовано 4M, перенос = 2.4M).

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestCarryoverCapped:
  output carry content decimal
  o scope Claude_family_pro.OverageComputation
scope TestCarryoverCapped:
  definition o.total_consumption equals 8000000.0
  definition o.carried_balance equals 0.0
  definition o.included_volume equals 12000000.0
  definition o.carryover_allowed equals true
  definition carry equals o.carryover_to_next
  assertion carry = 2400000.0
```

Последовательное списание: сначала перенос 1M, потом 12M, овераж = 14−12 = 2M.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestOverageWithCarry:
  output overage content decimal
  output carry content decimal
  o scope Claude_family_pro.OverageComputation
scope TestOverageWithCarry:
  definition o.total_consumption equals 15000000.0
  definition o.carried_balance equals 1000000.0
  definition o.included_volume equals 12000000.0
  definition o.carryover_allowed equals true
  definition overage equals o.overage
  definition carry equals o.carryover_to_next
  assertion overage = 2000000.0
  assertion carry = 0.0
```

Период расторжения: перенос не образуется (§4.3), даже если объём не выбран.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestNoCarryoverOnTermination:
  output carry content decimal
  o scope Claude_family_pro.OverageComputation
scope TestNoCarryoverOnTermination:
  definition o.total_consumption equals 5000000.0
  definition o.carried_balance equals 0.0
  definition o.included_volume equals 6000000.0
  definition o.carryover_allowed equals false
  definition carry equals o.carryover_to_next
  assertion carry = 0.0
```

## §3.1 + §5.1–5.3 — Тарификация овеража и скидки

Диапазон 1 (0–2M): скидки нет. Овераж 1M → gross $0.42/1000·1M = $420, скидка $0.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestChargeTier1:
  output gross content money
  output disc content money
  output after content money
  c scope Claude_family_pro.OverageCharge
scope TestChargeTier1:
  definition c.overage equals 1000000.0
  definition c.fair_use_excess equals 0.0
  definition gross equals c.gross_charge
  definition disc equals c.tier_discount
  definition after equals c.charge_after_tier
  assertion gross = $420.00
  assertion disc = $0.00
  assertion after = $420.00
```

Диапазон 2 (2–10M): овераж 7M → gross $2940, скидка 10% на 5M = $210, итог $2730.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestChargeTier2:
  output gross content money
  output disc content money
  output after content money
  c scope Claude_family_pro.OverageCharge
scope TestChargeTier2:
  definition c.overage equals 7000000.0
  definition c.fair_use_excess equals 0.0
  definition gross equals c.gross_charge
  definition disc equals c.tier_discount
  definition after equals c.charge_after_tier
  assertion gross = $2,940.00
  assertion disc = $210.00
  assertion after = $2,730.00
```

Диапазон 3 (>10M): овераж 12M → gross $5040, скидка 8M·10% + 2M·18% = $487.20.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestChargeTier3:
  output gross content money
  output disc content money
  output after content money
  c scope Claude_family_pro.OverageCharge
scope TestChargeTier3:
  definition c.overage equals 12000000.0
  definition c.fair_use_excess equals 0.0
  definition gross equals c.gross_charge
  definition disc equals c.tier_discount
  definition after equals c.charge_after_tier
  assertion gross = $5,040.00
  assertion disc = $487.20
  assertion after = $4,552.80
```

Порог лояльности (§5.2): овераж 25M ≥ 20M → единая 25%. gross $10500, скидка $2625.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestChargeLoyalty:
  output gross content money
  output disc content money
  output after content money
  c scope Claude_family_pro.OverageCharge
scope TestChargeLoyalty:
  definition c.overage equals 25000000.0
  definition c.fair_use_excess equals 0.0
  definition gross equals c.gross_charge
  definition disc equals c.tier_discount
  definition after equals c.charge_after_tier
  assertion gross = $10,500.00
  assertion disc = $2,625.00
  assertion after = $7,875.00
```

Fair use (§5.3): овераж 25M, из них 5M — потребление Участника свыше 30M (полная
ставка, без скидок). Скидочная база 20M, лояльность 25% → скидка $2100, итог $8400.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestChargeFairUse:
  output gross content money
  output disc content money
  output after content money
  c scope Claude_family_pro.OverageCharge
scope TestChargeFairUse:
  definition c.overage equals 25000000.0
  definition c.fair_use_excess equals 5000000.0
  definition gross equals c.gross_charge
  definition disc equals c.tier_discount
  definition after equals c.charge_after_tier
  assertion gross = $10,500.00
  assertion disc = $2,100.00
  assertion after = $8,400.00
```

## §5.4–5.5 — Стаж и реферальная

Только стаж (13-й период): 5% на $2730 = $136.50.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestTenureOnly:
  output combined content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.LoyaltyReferralDiscount
scope TestTenureOnly:
  definition d.charge_after_tier equals $2,730.00
  definition d.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition d.consecutive_paid_periods equals 13
  definition d.referral_active equals false
  definition combined equals d.combined_discount
  assertion combined = $136.50
```

Только реферальная: 20% на $2490 = $498.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestReferralOnly:
  output combined content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.LoyaltyReferralDiscount
scope TestReferralOnly:
  definition d.charge_after_tier equals $2,730.00
  definition d.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition d.consecutive_paid_periods equals 5
  definition d.referral_active equals true
  definition combined equals d.combined_discount
  assertion combined = $498.00
```

Оба основания (§5.5 — бо́льшая): max($136.50, $498) = $498.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestTenureAndReferral:
  output combined content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.LoyaltyReferralDiscount
scope TestTenureAndReferral:
  definition d.charge_after_tier equals $2,730.00
  definition d.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition d.consecutive_paid_periods equals 13
  definition d.referral_active equals true
  definition combined equals d.combined_discount
  assertion combined = $498.00
```

Ни одного основания: $0.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestNoLoyaltyDiscount:
  output combined content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.LoyaltyReferralDiscount
scope TestNoLoyaltyDiscount:
  definition d.charge_after_tier equals $2,730.00
  definition d.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition d.consecutive_paid_periods equals 5
  definition d.referral_active equals false
  definition combined equals d.combined_discount
  assertion combined = $0.00
```

## §5.6 + §2.3 — Потолок скидок и минимум

Без ограничений: скидка проходит, pretax = 2490 + 2940 − 210 = $5220.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestPretaxNormal:
  output total_disc content money
  output pretax content money
  s scope Claude_family_pro.DiscountCapAndTotal
scope TestPretaxNormal:
  definition s.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition s.gross_overage equals $2,940.00
  definition s.tier_discount equals $210.00
  definition s.combined_loyalty_referral equals $0.00
  definition s.is_termination equals false
  definition total_disc equals s.total_discount
  definition pretax equals s.pretax
  assertion total_disc = $210.00
  assertion pretax = $5,220.00
```

Потолок §5.6 срезает скидку И минимум §2.3 поднимает до платы: скидка 5000
режется до 30%·(2490+1000)=$1047, pretax_raw=2443 < 2490 → $2490.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestCapAndFloor:
  output total_disc content money
  output pretax content money
  s scope Claude_family_pro.DiscountCapAndTotal
scope TestCapAndFloor:
  definition s.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition s.gross_overage equals $1,000.00
  definition s.tier_discount equals $5,000.00
  definition s.combined_loyalty_referral equals $0.00
  definition s.is_termination equals false
  definition total_disc equals s.total_discount
  definition pretax equals s.pretax
  assertion total_disc = $1,047.00
  assertion pretax = $2,490.00
```

Минимум §2.3 без овеража: реферальная скидка $498 срезается полом до платы $2490.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestFloorNoOverage:
  output pretax content money
  s scope Claude_family_pro.DiscountCapAndTotal
scope TestFloorNoOverage:
  definition s.subscription_fee equals $2,490.00
  definition s.gross_overage equals $0.00
  definition s.tier_discount equals $0.00
  definition s.combined_loyalty_referral equals $498.00
  definition s.is_termination equals false
  definition pretax equals s.pretax
  assertion pretax = $2,490.00
```

Расторжение — минимум §2.3 НЕ применяется: pretax = прораченная плата $1245.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestNoFloorOnTermination:
  output pretax content money
  s scope Claude_family_pro.DiscountCapAndTotal
scope TestNoFloorOnTermination:
  definition s.subscription_fee equals $1,245.00
  definition s.gross_overage equals $0.00
  definition s.tier_discount equals $0.00
  definition s.combined_loyalty_referral equals $0.00
  definition s.is_termination equals true
  definition pretax equals s.pretax
  assertion pretax = $1,245.00
```

