```

## §8 — НДС и итог

Обычный: taxable $5220, НДС 20% = $1044, итог $6264.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestFinalNormal:
  output vat content money
  output total content money
  f scope Claude_family_pro.FinalBill
scope TestFinalNormal:
  definition f.pretax equals $5,220.00
  definition f.compensation equals $0.00
  definition f.vat_rate equals 0.20
  definition vat equals f.vat_amount
  definition total equals f.total_due
  assertion vat = $1,044.00
  assertion total = $6,264.00
```

Компенсация уменьшает базу НДС: taxable 2490−249 = 2241, итог 2241·1.2 = $2689.20.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestFinalWithComp:
  output total content money
  f scope Claude_family_pro.FinalBill
scope TestFinalWithComp:
  definition f.pretax equals $2,490.00
  definition f.compensation equals $249.00
  definition f.vat_rate equals 0.20
  definition total equals f.total_due
  assertion total = $2,689.20
```

Компенсация больше пред-налоговой суммы: база не уходит в минус → итог $0.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestFinalCompExceeds:
  output total content money
  f scope Claude_family_pro.FinalBill
scope TestFinalCompExceeds:
  definition f.pretax equals $2,490.00
  definition f.compensation equals $2,490.00
  definition f.vat_rate equals 0.20
  definition total equals f.total_due
  assertion total = $0.00
```

## §6 — Разнесение по Участникам

Инвариант всех тестов разнесения: сумма всех начислений = начислению Группы.

Чистое деление (без остатка, без детей): $99 на 60M/30M/10M → A=$29.70, B=$9.90,
Владелец = 99 − 39.60 = $59.40.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDistClean:
  output owner content money
  output alloc_sum content money
  output a_charge content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.ParticipantDistribution
scope TestDistClean:
  definition d.group_charge equals $99.00
  definition d.members equals [
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 1 -- normalized: 60000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: true};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 2 -- normalized: 30000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 3 -- normalized: 10000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false}
  ]
  definition owner equals d.owner_charge
  definition alloc_sum equals Money.sum of (map each c among d.allocations to c.charge)
  definition a_charge equals
    Money.sum of (map each c among d.allocations to
      (if c.member_id = 2 then c.charge else $0.00))
  assertion owner = $59.40
  assertion a_charge = $29.70
  assertion alloc_sum = $99.00
```

Остаток округления вниз относится на Владельца: $100 на три равные доли → каждому
$33.33, Владелец забирает остаток $0.01 → $33.34.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDistRemainder:
  output owner content money
  output alloc_sum content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.ParticipantDistribution
scope TestDistRemainder:
  definition d.group_charge equals $100.00
  definition d.members equals [
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 1 -- normalized: 1.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: true};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 2 -- normalized: 1.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 3 -- normalized: 1.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false}
  ]
  definition owner equals d.owner_charge
  definition alloc_sum equals Money.sum of (map each c among d.allocations to c.charge)
  assertion owner = $33.34
  assertion alloc_sum = $100.00
```

Детский аккаунт (§6.3): его доля относится на Владельца. $90, доли 10M/20M(дет)/10M
→ обычный B = 90·10/40 = $22.50, ребёнок $0, Владелец = 90 − 22.50 = $67.50.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDistChild:
  output owner content money
  output child_charge content money
  output alloc_sum content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.ParticipantDistribution
scope TestDistChild:
  definition d.group_charge equals $90.00
  definition d.members equals [
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 1 -- normalized: 10000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: true};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 2 -- normalized: 20000000.0 -- is_child: true -- is_owner: false};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 3 -- normalized: 10000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false}
  ]
  definition owner equals d.owner_charge
  definition child_charge equals
    Money.sum of (map each c among d.allocations to
      (if c.member_id = 2 then c.charge else $0.00))
  definition alloc_sum equals Money.sum of (map each c among d.allocations to c.charge)
  assertion child_charge = $0.00
  assertion owner = $67.50
  assertion alloc_sum = $90.00
```

Нулевое потребление: всё начисление на Владельца (деления на ноль нет).

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDistZero:
  output owner content money
  d scope Claude_family_pro.ParticipantDistribution
scope TestDistZero:
  definition d.group_charge equals $50.00
  definition d.members equals [
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 1 -- normalized: 0.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: true};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 2 -- normalized: 0.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false}
  ]
  definition owner equals d.owner_charge
  assertion owner = $50.00
```

## Сквозной расчёт GroupPeriodBill

Обычный период: Группа 8M+6M = 14M, овераж 2M, плата $2490, НДС 20%.
gross $840, скидок нет, pretax $3330, НДС $666, итог $3996; разнос $1902.86 / $1427.14.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEndToEndNormal:
  output overage content decimal
  output pretax content money
  output total content money
  output owner content money
  g scope Claude_family_pro.GroupPeriodBill
scope TestEndToEndNormal:
  definition g.members equals [
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 1 -- normalized: 8000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: true};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 2 -- normalized: 6000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: false}
  ]
  definition g.carried_balance equals 0.0
  definition g.is_termination equals false
  definition g.active_days equals 30
  definition g.days_in_month equals 30
  definition g.consecutive_paid_periods equals 5
  definition g.referral_active equals false
  definition g.availability equals 0.999
  definition g.vat_rate equals 0.20
  definition overage equals g.overage
  definition pretax equals g.pretax
  definition total equals g.total_due
  definition owner equals g.owner_charge
  assertion overage = 2000000.0
  assertion pretax = $3,330.00
  assertion total = $3,996.00
  assertion owner = $1,902.86
```

Крупный период: Владелец 35M + детский 5M. Овераж 28M (≥20M, лояльность), fair use
5M, стаж (13-й период) и реферальная → берётся реферальная $498, SLA 97% → $747.
gross $11760, скидка $2415+$498=$2913, pretax $11337, НДС $2118, итог $12708;
ребёнок в разнос не идёт → всё на Владельца $11337.

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEndToEndLoyalty:
  output overage content decimal
  output gross content money
  output total_disc content money
  output pretax content money
  output comp content money
  output total content money
  output owner content money
  g scope Claude_family_pro.GroupPeriodBill
scope TestEndToEndLoyalty:
  definition g.members equals [
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 1 -- normalized: 35000000.0 -- is_child: false -- is_owner: true};
    Claude_family_pro.Member{-- member_id: 2 -- normalized: 5000000.0 -- is_child: true -- is_owner: false}
  ]
  definition g.carried_balance equals 0.0
  definition g.is_termination equals false
  definition g.active_days equals 30
  definition g.days_in_month equals 30
  definition g.consecutive_paid_periods equals 13
  definition g.referral_active equals true
